config PWM_NUMAKER
	bool "Nuvoton NUMAKER MCU PWM driver"
	depends on SOC_FAMILY_NUMAKER
    select HAS_NUMAKER_PWM
    default y
	help
	  This option enables the PWM driver for Nuvoton NUMAKER family of processors. Say y if you wish to enable NUMAKER PWM.

